<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kiểm tra Email - Smart House</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #004487 0%, #1E90FF 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .card-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 450px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card-container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        }

        .brand h1 {
            font-size: 2.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .brand p {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .icon-wrapper {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00bfff, #0066cc);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .icon-wrapper i {
            font-size: 50px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.5);
            }

            70% {
                transform: scale(1.05);
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 20px rgba(0, 191, 255, 0);
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(0, 191, 255, 0);
            }
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066cc 0%, #00bfff 100%);
            border: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 91, 187, 0.35);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #004080 0%, #0099ff 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-outline-secondary {
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .text-muted {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="card-container">
        <div class="brand">
            <h1>
                <span style="color:#00bfff;">Air</span>
                <span style="color:#ffc107;">Quality</span>
            </h1>
            <p>Kiểm tra email để tiếp tục đặt lại mật khẩu</p>
        </div>

        <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <i class="bi bi-envelope-open-fill"></i>
        </div>

        <p>
            Liên kết đặt lại mật khẩu đã được gửi đến email của bạn.<br>
            Vui lòng kiểm tra hộp thư và làm theo hướng dẫn.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted">
            Nếu không tìm thấy, hãy kiểm tra thư mục Spam hoặc nhấn “Gửi lại email”.
        </p>

        <a href="/auth/forgot-password" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Gửi lại email</a>
        <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline-secondary w-100">Quay lại đăng nhập</a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>